---
title: Seared Double Duck in Orange-Apricot Sauce with Almonds and Rosemary Roasted Potatoes
description: Juicy duck breasts are seared until the skin is crispy and golden-brown, then drizzled with mouthwatering orange-apricot sauce. The potatoes complement the tart sauce and a crisp salad finishes off a luxurious meal!
